{"tid":1740330,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"傳港交所競購西班牙交易所 市值達256億元","createTime":"2019-11-20T01:52:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T18:06:11.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"45ae688754d90cc189830c2d4de4b2937785aa0c","tid":1740330,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:52:33.000Z","msg":"【新增內容】西班牙報紙《五日報》引述金融業內消息人士指，港交所（388）正考慮競標收購西班牙證券市場公司Bolsas y Mercados Espanoles，港交所發言人表示不評論併購傳聞。<br />\n<br />\nBME旗下有四間證交所，於馬德里證交所上市，目前市值超過29.5億歐元（約255.8億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n泛歐交易所已證實與BME就潛在收購正進行磋商。瑞士證交所亦於周一（18日）宣佈，已向BME提出收購要約，擬以每股34歐元收購其全部股權，涉資242.7億港元。近日併購消息刺激BME股價急漲，由上周五收市價25.4歐元，升近40%至目前的35.26歐元，創一年新高。<br />\n<br />\n早前港交所向倫交所提出併購建議，雖放棄告終，但該所主席史美倫曾明言不排除將來會併購其他交易所。值得留意的是，就提購倫交所一事，港交所仍需支付高達1.3億港元的相關費用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191119/60286414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60286414&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=97b59731\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191119%2F60286414&h=af720621\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20191119/60286414</a>"},{"pid":"29e4960760920273ad049a3634d98d4d0fd4f6d2","tid":1740330,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:53:03.000Z","msg":"如果你覺得勇武暫時要休息，咁作為和理非嘅你請今晚出場，今晚有行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1740320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1740320</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1f4fdf9c03e5d0f465b4a0907f39b2ef21c98f43","tid":1740330,"uid":22243,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T01:53:26.000Z","msg":"中共周鳩圍買交易所想搵第二個香港？"},{"pid":"25d62f1e6127cbcfe343f4c672806b05b5f51423","tid":1740330,"uid":17503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1f4fdf9c03e5d0f465b4a0907